text: Rhett & Link are an American comedy duo with Rhett McLaughlin (born October 11, 1977) and Charles Lincoln "Link" Neal (born June 1, 1978). They call themselves "Internetainers" (portmanteau of "Internet" and "entertainers"). They are known for creating and hosting the YouTube series Good mythical morning. Their other known projects include comedic songs and sketches, Independent Film Channel series Rhett & Link: Commercial Kings, and their YouTube Premium series Rhett and Link's Buddy System (Season 1 and Season 2). Rhett was born in Macon, Georgia. Link was born in Boone Trail, North Carolina.
